      <title>英美资源集团以 38 亿美元收购 Peabody 煤炭业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/anglo-agrees-to-sell-the-rest-of-its-steelmaking-coal-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着矿业公司重组步伐加快，英美资源集团同意将其炼钢煤业务出售给 Peabody Energy Corp.，交易价格可能高达 37.8 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/anglo-agrees-to-sell-the-rest-of-its-steelmaking-coal-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 07:10:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
